    "attributes": {
        "action": "Limit the school week to three days",
        "additional_details": "Given the current cost of living crisis, and high levels of inflation, we believe it would be better for schools to focus on delivering high-quality education for a three-day week, rather than struggling with the cost of continuing to remain open five days a week. This should reduce energy costs for schools, and travel costs for teachers.",
        "background": "We want the Government to shorten the school week to three days, from the current five.",
